  "_comment": "Selector map captured via `asm recon` 2026-06-18. area -> { _default, seoul, busan } -> key -> CSS string OR {css, desc}. The optional desc enables AUTONOMOUS self-heal: when the css no longer resolves, the healer re-locates the element from these stable semantic anchors (name/label/type/value/btnText) and writes the new css to the gitignored override layer. Plain-string entries are unchanged (no heal). desc fields (all optional): label(Korean), name(HTML name attr), tag, type, value(radio/checkbox), optionSet[], btnText, onclick(fn), form(scoping form id), frame, consume('locator'|'querySelector'|'both'), criticality('high'=>always Tier-2, never auto). Re-run recon + `asm heal` when the site changes; never hand-edit the override layer.",
